            <title>[BOOKKEEPER-19] BookKeeper doesn&apos;t support more than 2Gig of memory</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BOOKKEEPER-19</link>
                <project id="12311293" key="BOOKKEEPER">Bookkeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;From LedgerCache.java&lt;br/&gt;
    private static int pageLimit = (int)(Runtime.getRuntime().maxMemory() / 3) / LedgerEntryPage.PAGE_SIZE;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;pageLimit will be negative is maxMemory is 2^31 or more. This causes exceptions later on when pageLimit is used.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
