                            <comment id="13035354" author="ikelly" created="Wed, 18 May 2011 14:01:12 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Simple fix. Also fixed a style error as pageCount was never initialised.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13035381" author="ikelly" created="Wed, 18 May 2011 14:36:41 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Actually, maxMemory &amp;gt;= 6G is the problem as we divide by 3. Writing a test for this would be a pain, as it a) requires everyone to have 8G memory, and b) requires a custom launcher for the jvm.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
